{"tid":1061334,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"豬界傳奇！天才「豬卡索」超有才華　一幅畫賣台幣12萬","createTime":"2019-03-14T10:28:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-14T10:54:58.000Z","uid":32511,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4bfe97b5d71d7718d2af831a8815fcdabee39c39","tid":1061334,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T10:28:54.000Z","msg":"豬界傳奇！來自南非的天才「豬卡索」（Pigcasso）超會「畫畫」，2016年被主人橋安（Joanne Lefson）從屠宰場救出來，之後意外發現牠懂得叼起油漆刷，於是靈機一動拿出畫布讓牠作畫，沒想到作品非常好看，也讓牠意外獲得高人氣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/03/14/1824744-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F03%2F14%2F1824744-XXL.jpg&h=1ef1ba4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/03/14/1824743-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F03%2F14%2F1824743-XXL.jpg&h=6a6953c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n身為最特別的畫家，豬卡索不僅成為媒體的新寵兒，更被瑞士品牌Swatch看重，邀請牠設計手錶錶盤，豬卡索也不負眾望完成任務。最近牠的一幅畫更賣出4000美元（約12.3萬台幣）的高價。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/03/14/1824742-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F03%2F14%2F1824742-XXL.jpg&h=f1cc1faa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一幅畫能拍出高價不是沒有原因的，「豬卡索」的畫作色彩豐富，對比鮮明並且充滿活力，很難想像這些作品是出自「豬口」，牠咬著畫筆忘情的揮灑創作，認真投入的模樣更讓人留下深刻的印象。"},{"pid":"bf990db411e9d0db7ad44b00da5e45b7805ea3f9","tid":1061334,"uid":36383,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T10:31:49.000Z","msg":"唔洗比人劏，唔怪得啲畫色彩斑斕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a983f8303207715659b28e7cdf3fc346a6358c9e","tid":1061334,"uid":165336,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T10:32:35.000Z","msg":"靚過我畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3bb6fd64b676748729dc298454628f3e68a16f6","tid":1061334,"uid":96617,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a983f8303207715659b28e7cdf3fc346a6358c9e","tid":1061334,"uid":165336,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T10:32:35.000Z","msg":"靚過我畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T10:35:54.000Z","msg":"屌我都覺得靚過自己畫<br />\n喊出來"},{"pid":"9b8a2a161440481fd85cedf2e4d22952d70af0e8","tid":1061334,"uid":36995,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T10:42:04.000Z","msg":"Pi<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">g</span>casso<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54966cbb66a4c0429dd4604d0204b9869859d2dd","tid":1061334,"uid":81273,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T10:42:35.000Z","msg":"屌 最尾果張真係有料到架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42148a350e6a5986311b7d6b727f29bb981125ae","tid":1061334,"uid":59832,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9b8a2a161440481fd85cedf2e4d22952d70af0e8","tid":1061334,"uid":36995,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T10:42:04.000Z","msg":"Pi<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">g</span>casso<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T10:43:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />casso"},{"pid":"8d03ecb8671142436a1140df7bc5473f780dd86e","tid":1061334,"uid":68902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T10:43:38.000Z","msg":"屌，連隻豬搵錢能力都咁高 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"449298699acdcf22dccac59e3cedf54a1b6d257e","tid":1061334,"uid":28641,"like":0